## 3. Field Equations

Evolution equations for the three-field system:

```
dα/dt  = κ_a ∇²α  −  α_restore (α − 1)  +  g_sa (|σ| − σ_min)  +  g_an ν

dσ/dt  = κ_s ∇²σ  +  pot_term  +  g_local (α − 1) σ/|σ|  +  g_sn ν σ/|σ|

dν/dt  = κ_n ∇²ν  −  γ_n ν  −  g_sat ν³
         +  dim_gain · g_an (α − 1)
         +  dim_gain · g_sn (|σ| − σ_min)

dJ/dt  = −j_decay · J  +  j_alpha (α − 1) J  +  dim_gain · g_jn ν²
```

where:

```
pot_term  = −(dV/d|σ|) · σ/|σ|
dV/d|σ|   = −2 μ² |σ|  +  4 λ |σ|³
g_local   = g_as · exp(−local_stress / stress_threshold)
local_stress = |α − 1| + ||σ| − σ_min|
```

